rows.label: qst400105_msg0001
rows.name:
This is the new cylinder, mo. Please
test it at the nearby Salvage Point
and tell me what you think, mo.

rows.label: qst400105_msg0002
rows.name: Got it! Leave it to me!

rows.label: qst400105_msg0003
rows.name:
Please test the new cylinder
at the Salvage Point at the
end of this pier, mo.

rows.label: qst400105_msg0004
rows.name:
Looks like you're finished, mo.
How was the new cylinder, mo?

rows.label: qst400105_msg0009
rows.name:
Fantastic, mo? That's great!
Other salvagers will be
happy to hear that, mo!

rows.label: qst400105_msg0010
rows.name: Okay, mo...!? What a vague answer, mo!

rows.label: qst400105_msg0011
rows.name:
But I suppose it takes a few tries
to get used to a new cylinder, mo.

rows.label: qst400105_msg0012
rows.name:
Are you sure it wasn't just your luck,
mo? This is a bargain cylinder that
should get good treasure for anyone, mo.

rows.label: qst400105_msg0013
rows.name:
In any case, thank you
for your help, mo.

rows.label: qst400105_msg0014
rows.name:
And when that one runs out,
I hope you'll come to my
shop to buy more, mo!

rows.label: qst400105_msg0015
rows.name:
As thanks, here's a normal
cylinder, mo. You can salvage
from the same spot, mo!
